{"tid":1422894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"專業關公 記者會 歡迎Q&A","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T04:02:28.000Z","uid":289620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"298651ae153397c795bd0308c5e543afea740e5c","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:17:43.000Z","msg":"新聞稿<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於近日香港出現頻繁事件，政府未有全民聆聽社會各位聲音，未有急市民所急，解市民之憂，反而選擇浪費公帑每日舉行內容空泛的記者招待會。<br />\n<br />\n一眾熱心市民故特此舉辦民間記者會，期望透過不同平台收集各方意見，歸納重點，讓大眾市民可以接收全全面資訊，讓政府可以早日對症下藥，回復社會安寧。"},{"pid":"32004518620cadf3cb4cde46ac3cdb1fdea73ab3","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:20:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"dabc2d66a873788a72e063de6448a8ce49445ab3","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:20:29.000Z","msg":"推到有人問"},{"pid":"954be99afd7144d0d8936cfdeb23e4f205dadaac","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"包保正經答<br />\n方向會跟我前post<br />\n<br />\n今日發布會 少少意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1421797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1421797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94c3cc613f48beb60e1c4dedfaec3791b8040462","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"49b6c74f4cce0e596513ae18eb4658cd23652b1f","tid":1422894,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eebcd9c29e5f470d5b55142b4f62ce541d203702","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:24:42.000Z","msg":"真關公 十年經驗"},{"pid":"5cef057c016a8f4b842eada456c31713817cc306","tid":1422894,"uid":289620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c